nstAgentModuleObject.name: nstAgentModuleObject
nstAgentModuleObject.description: This is an object that simply supports a writable integer when compiled into the agent. See http://www.net-snmp.org/tutorial-5/toolkit/XXX for further implementation details.

nstAgentSubagentObject.name: nstAgentSubagentObject
nstAgentSubagentObject.description: This is an object that simply supports a writable integer when attached to the agent. The object should be accessible when the agentx subagent containing this object is attached. See http://www.net-snmp.org/tutorial-5/toolkit/XXX for further implementation details.

nstAgentPluginObject.name: nstAgentPluginObject
nstAgentPluginObject.description: This is an object that simply supports a writable integer when attached to the agent. This object should be accessible when the dynamic plugin has been loaded into the agent. See http://www.net-snmp.org/tutorial-5/toolkit/XXX for further implementation details.
